sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Visitor
    participant ServicesPage as Services Page UI
    participant BookingCta as Booking CTA Component
    participant ContactForm as Contact Form UI
    participant MsgAPI as POST /api/messages
    participant DB as PostgreSQL (Prisma)
    participant Dashboard as Dashboard Messages

    Visitor->>ServicesPage: Open /services
    ServicesPage->>BookingCta: Render CTA actions
    Visitor->>BookingCta: Click "Book a discovery call"
    BookingCta->>ContactForm: Navigate to contact intake flow

    Visitor->>ContactForm: Submit project requirements
    ContactForm->>MsgAPI: Create intake message
    MsgAPI->>DB: Insert MESSAGE with source=services-booking
    DB-->>MsgAPI: Created row
    MsgAPI-->>ContactForm: 201 Created
    ContactForm-->>Visitor: Booking request confirmation

    Dashboard->>MsgAPI: GET /api/messages?source=services-booking
    MsgAPI->>DB: Query booking-origin leads
    DB-->>MsgAPI: Booking lead queue
    MsgAPI-->>Dashboard: Render prioritized intake list
